data.description: Holy smokes, if its space you are looking for, than look no further.  This home has been lovingly cared for and has an entire separate in-law suite with its own sunroom, living room, kitchen, laundry room and master bedroom.  Private access to the backyard and to the pool area off this addition.  All of the repairs have already been done for you (see attached document for description).  Theses are just a few reasons why the sellers have loved this home for so many years.  Great neighborhood with plenty of privacy with the convenience of being on a cul-de-sac.  Extremely close proximity to shopping, restaurants, and the interstate.  The pool speaks for itself.  And if that doesn't cool you off enough in the summer heat, than the beautiful mature hardwoods on the property helps when you seek shade.  This house truly embodies what you envision a "HOME" to be.  Come see for yourself.
